                      <origin>
                             <origDate notBefore="1700" notAfter="1799">18th century.</origDate>
                             The manuscript seems to have been composed of tree production units.
                             Two of them, <ref target="#p2"/> and <ref target="#p3"/> are linked to the same commissioner,
                             <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13808QerebtaKrestos">Qǝrǝbta Krǝstos</persName>. It is not clear if any of three
                             were meant as circulation units. The binding seems to fit best the smallest one, <ref target="#p1"/>.
                    </origin>
